# Unity Survival System

A Unity gameplay prototype focused on survival mechanics, AI systems, and player interaction features.

## Features

- Player Movement System
- Enemy AI Behavior
- Inventory System
- Health & Survival Mechanics
- Interaction System
- UI Elements
- Day & Night Cycle
- Optimized Gameplay Systems

## Built With

- Unity Engine
- C#
- Visual Studio

## Project Goal

This project was created to improve gameplay programming skills and develop polished survival-style mechanics using Unity.

## Scripts Included

- PlayerController.cs
- EnemyAI.cs
- InventorySystem.cs
- HealthSystem.cs
- InteractionSystem.cs
- DayNightCycle.cs

## Future Improvements

- Advanced Enemy Behaviors
- Crafting System
- Save & Load System
- Multiplayer Support
- Better UI/UX

## Developer

KaifInteractive  
Unity Game Developer focused on gameplay systems, AI, survival mechanics, and optimization.

## Repository Purpose

This repository showcases Unity gameplay programming and survival system development for learning, portfolio, and collaboration purposes.
